01:34:37.170 --> 01:34:40.104
- It's on the ticket.
- It was demolished two years ago.

01:34:40.106 --> 01:34:42.042
♪

01:34:49.483 --> 01:34:51.385
[Harvey laughing]

01:34:56.088 --> 01:34:58.388
