and with no friends.

01:35:34.293 --> 01:35:36.527
- Fuck you!
- Yeah, fuck you too.

01:35:36.529 --> 01:35:39.363
[Harvey laughs]

01:35:39.365 --> 01:35:41.799
So I'm the liar, right?
You don't... you don't have...

01:35:41.801 --> 01:35:43.433
Yes, you're a liar!
