01:36:49.636 --> 01:36:52.173
♪

01:37:22.969 --> 01:37:24.171
[sobs]

01:37:58.203 --> 01:38:00.474
[typewriter clacking]

01:38:04.577 --> 01:38:08.646
[Harvey] <i>I believe the deceased
should be protected</i>

01:38:08.648 --> 01:38:11.418
